function swap_spritesheet(s)
 for yy=0,127 do
  for xx=0,127 do
   local n=0
   local s=sub(s,xx+yy*128+1,xx+yy*128+1)
   n=("0x"..s)+0
   sset(xx,yy,n)
  end
 end
end

function draw_lpack(_pack,lpx,lpy)
 for yy=0,63 do
		for xx=1,64 do
			pset(lpx+xx,lpy+yy,tonum(_pack[xx+64*yy],1))
		end
	end
		spr(21,lpx+16,lpy+66)
end

function sprite_to_string()
 a=""
 for yy=64,127 do
  for xx=0,63 do
   local n=sget(xx,yy)
   if (n==0) s = "0"
   if(n==1) s = "1"
   if(n==2) s = "2"
   if(n==3) s = "3"
   if(n==4) s = "4"
   if(n==5) s = "5"
   if(n==6) s = "6"
   if(n==7) s = "7"
   if(n==8) s = "8"
   if(n==9) s = "9"
   if(n==10) s = "a"
   if(n==11) s = "b"
   if(n==12) s = "c"
   if(n==13) s = "d"
   if(n==14) s = "e"
   if(n==15) s = "f"
   a=a..s
  end
 end
 printh(a,"@clip")
end

function _init()
	sprite_to_string()
